        <section class="max-w-6xl w-full">
            <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-display mb-12 text-center">
                WE'D LOVE TO HEAR FROM YOU
            </h1>
            <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-8 opacity-90">
                Got feedback? Questions? Or just feel like yelling at us because you forgot your own password?  
                Go ahead â€” we'll read it, probably.
            </p>
            
            <div class="mb-8">
